        "timestamp": "2018-07-18 23:12:50.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nCan we split this change. \n\nWe need to isolate the changes to the global files from the project specific yamls. \n\nWhy do we need to duplicate the already existing jobs in \tjjb/global-templates-java.yaml?\nCan we use the ones we have already? I am working into reducing the amount of templates we have.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "1c38120938baea7a5b8a8a0e3787505fbcdba3f4",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 35,
          "name": "Gary Wu",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "gary.wu@gmail.com",
          "username": "gwu"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-07-18 23:17:43.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis is because many jobs use the original template, and we're trying to gradually migrate some of those jobs to a new template without changing the job names.  Also, not all of these jobs are eligible to migrate to the new template, so we might need to live with both for a while.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
